author: Epic Games
description:
Step into the dugout in Football Manager 26 now. https://epic.gm/fm26

Explore a reimagined user interface, develop advanced tactical systems through the addition of In and Out of Possession formations, and build your dream squad with more intelligent recruitment tools powered by TransferRoom.

Lead men’s or women’s teams into the most immersive Match Day in series history, with upgraded on-pitch visuals and animations captured from real-life matches.

FM26 is the legacy, redefined.

With a new engine bringing new possibilities for enhanced storytelling, you’re not just playing the game. You’re shaping the future of football.
title: Football Manager 26 | Available Now

author: Epic Games
description:
Fresh Fish for Farmers! Farming Simulator 25: Highlands Fishing is now available on the Epic Games Store to grant the popular series a whole new gameplay feature! 

Available as Expansion and Edition (bundled with the main game). https://epic.gm/fs25-highland-fishing
title: Farming Simulator 25 - Highlands Fishing | Launch
